dc_description_s: Popluation of Placer County California and surrounding areas. This dataset contains Census counts from 2000 and 2010. It also conatins estimated 2016 population (Source: ESRI, 2016) and population projections for 2021 (source: ESRI, 2016). This dataset is aggregated to the cenusus tract level.
